profile:
Fernand Boileau is a third generation cabinet maker and has been in this trade for over 30 years. Before going into permanent retirement, he decided to establish Boiserie SEBO Woodwork Inc. in February 2004, with the help of his two sons, Sebastien and Mathieu. He is quite proud of his achievements and first and foremost this family business.

We design, build and install custom cabinetry for kitchens and bathrooms, as well as entertainment centers and other furniture. Whether you’re planning a simple project or looking for a turn key renovation, we’ve got you covered.

Boiserie Sebo Woodwork Inc is located in Orleans. Our beautiful showroom contains an array of kitchens, vanities, bar, wine cellar and a wide array of doors and materials. The plant has been equipped with the most modern equipment to insure precision and the highest quality end product. We choose only the highest grade of materials to ensure the quality and longevity of our product.

Our experienced designers work one on one with you to create the ideal customized space to fit your budget and style. We offer free consultations, which includes them going to your home for measurements, a floor plan layout complete with 3d views of your completed project, and a price breakdown.
products: Custom cabinets, granite/quartz countertops, laminate countertops, LED lighting, Outdoor cabinets
